snippet.title: Amber Heard: Who Is? | Things You Didn't Know |
snippet.description:
This is the story of Amber Laura Heard, an American actress, and model. She made her film debut in a minor supporting role in the sports drama Friday Night Lights (2004), followed by a series of other small roles in television and film. Her first leading role was in the horror film All the Boys Love Mandy Lane (2006). Her second major role came in the short-running The CW television series Hidden Palms (2007). Amber Heard, former wife of Johnny Depp. For more interesting and exclusive stories about your favorite personalities, subscribe to People Exclusive.
